---
import RegisterButton from './RegisterButton.astro';
---
<section class="section">
  <div class="container text-block" style="text-align: center;">
    <h2>How to turn your Facebook Ads into enrolments.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 18px;">
      This is a free, no-pitch, system-led session. You'll leave knowing exactly what a working
      enrolment funnel looks like - and where yours is leaking right now.
    </p>
    <div style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
      <RegisterButton />
    </div>
    <p style="font-size: var(--font-size-small); color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-md);">
      Limited live attendance. Recording sent to all registrants.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
